TY  - JOUR
T1  - Confidence Intervals for Projections of Partially Identified Parameters
AU  - Kaido, Hiroaki
AU  - Molinari, Francesca
AU  - Stoye, Jörg
Y1  - 2019/07/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/07/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA14075
